---
title: Chicken with Mushroom Marinara plus Roasted Potato & Bell Pepper Jumble
description: Pork chops may be basic (we like to say “classic”),  but they never have to be boring! Especially these juicy, satisfying chops topped with lots of garlicky mushroom-studded marinara sauce. Fresh Fam, you know by now: It’s all about that powerhouse pan sauce! Tender roasted bell peppers and half-moon potatoes complete the plate for a dinner idea that’s filling, flavorful, and a far cry from your everyday “other white meat.”
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/674e30eca0d670a6c9693b0c-e7a76601.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6750da84deb6306cae775ef9-en-US.pdf
